	RenderElementObjPtr.

	* Track.cxx:
	* Track.h:
	Added optional TrackRnrStyle* argument to TrackList constructors;
	renamed mRnrStyle to fRnrStyle.

2006-10-02  Matevz Tadel  <matevz.tadel@cern.ch>

	EVE-dev

	* .SKEL-ged.cxx:
	* .SKEL-ged.h:
	* .SKEL-gl.cxx:
	* .SKEL-gl.h:
	* .SKEL.h:
