	* LinkDef.h:
	* Reve.h:
	New class Reve::ReferenceCount; to be used as secondary base class.

2006-05-15  Matevz Tadel  <matevz.tadel@cern.ch>

	EVE-dev branch

	* Reve.cxx:
	* Reve.h:
	New function ColorFromIdx().

	* BoxSet.cxx:
	* BoxSet.h:
	* BoxSetGL.cxx:
	* BoxSetGL.h:
	New files: a set of boxes with direct GL rendering.

